<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1240</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yīn wèi cóng tóu yī tiān qǐ zhí dào rú jīn,
 nǐ men shì tóng xīn hé yì de, tóng xīn hé yì xìng wàng fú yīn.
 wèi nǐ men yǒu zhè yàng de yì niàn, cháng cháng gǎn xiè fù shén.
 zài zhǔ lǐ jì niàn nǐ men, qiè qiè xiǎng niàn nǐ men.
 yīn wèi wǒ men shì tóng lù rén, wǒ men shì yī jiā rén.
 xiāng qīn xiāng ài de yī jiā rén, chóu dí dōu jù pà shí fēn.
 yīn wèi cóng tóu yī tiān qǐ zhí dào rú jīn,
 wǒ men tóng xīn hé yì xìng wàng fú yīn. yán zhe zhǔ de biāo gān xiàng qián jìn.</lyrics>
<title>yīn wèi cóng tóu yī tiān qǐ zhí dào rú jīn 迦南1240</title>
</song>